# University descriptions
msgid "Ireland's largest university. Strong research culture, vibrant campus life and excellent transport links to the city centre."
msgstr "爱尔兰最大的大学。强大的研究文化、充满活力的校园生活以及通往市中心的出色交通联系。"

msgid "Consistently ranked among Ireland's top universities for graduate employment. Modern campus with purpose-built student accommodation on-site."
msgstr "始终跻身爱尔兰应届毕业生就业率最高的大学之列。现代化校园，设有专门建造的学生住宿。"

msgid "Ireland's first technological university. Located in a landmark regeneration quarter in the heart of Dublin, minutes from the city centre."
msgstr "爱尔兰第一所技术大学。位于都柏林市中心的标志性再生区，距市中心仅几分钟路程。"

msgid "Founded in 1592, Trinity is Ireland's oldest and most prestigious university. Located in the city centre, accommodation nearby is in high demand."
msgstr "三一学院成立于1592年，是爱尔兰历史最悠久、最负盛名的大学。位于市中心，附近住宿供不应求。"

msgid "A welcoming university town campus 25 km west of Dublin. Known for its friendly community atmosphere and affordable accommodation options."
msgstr "位于都柏林以西25公里的热情大学城校园。以友好的社区氛围和实惠的住宿选择而闻名。"

msgid "One of Ireland's leading research universities, set on a stunning Victorian campus. Cork city offers a lively student scene and lower living costs."
msgstr "爱尔兰领先的研究型大学之一，坐落在令人叹为观止的维多利亚式校园内。科克市提供充满活力的学生环境和较低的生活成本。"

msgid "A dynamic campus university on the banks of the River Shannon. Known for its co-operative education programme and strong industry links."
msgstr "坐落在香农河畔的充满活力的校园大学。以其合作教育计划和强大的行业联系而闻名。"

msgid "Located in the heart of one of Ireland's most vibrant cities. Renowned for its bilingual character, arts culture and thriving student community."
msgstr "位于爱尔兰最具活力的城市之一的中心。以其双语特色、艺术文化和蓬勃发展的学生社区而闻名。"
